SKATE AND DESTROY CANCER! Get this shirt and watch the film to support @grindforlifeorg ! @kindhumans_movement created a tee that helps provide financial support for those fighting cancer and collaborated with @gopro on a rad film that tells Mike Roger's amazing story of beating cancer twice and starting this amazing org. 
Watch the full film on GoPro's youtube (LINK IN BIO), support at grindforlife.org and get the T-Shirt at kindhumans.com (LINK IN BIO)

#Kindhumans #GrindforLife #GoProForACause #CollabForKindness
